<Window
    x:Class="XIVLauncher.Windows.CustomMessageBox"
    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
    xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
    xmlns:materialDesign="http://materialdesigninxaml.net/winfx/xaml/themes"
    xmlns:mahIcon="http://metro.mahapps.com/winfx/xaml/iconpacks"
    xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
    Title="XIVLauncher Error"
    Width="Auto"
    Height="Auto"
    Background="{DynamicResource MaterialDesign.Brush.Background}"
    Icon="pack://application:,,,/Resources/dalamud_icon.ico"
    ResizeMode="NoResize"
    SizeToContent="WidthAndHeight"
    TextElement.Foreground="{DynamicResource MaterialDesign.Brush.Foreground}"
    WindowStartupLocation="CenterScreen"
    mc:Ignorable="d">
    <Grid MouseMove="CustomMessageBox_MouseMove">
        <StackPanel
            Orientation="Horizontal" Margin="10 10 10 50">
            <materialDesign:PackIcon Kind="AlertOctagon" HorizontalAlignment="Stretch" VerticalAlignment="Top"
                                     Width="30"
                                     Height="30" Foreground="Red" Margin="0,0,10,0" x:Name="ErrorPackIcon" />
            <StackPanel Orientation="Vertical" Width="540" MinHeight="100">
                <Grid MinHeight="30">
                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" x:Name="MessageTextBlock" VerticalAlignment="Center">
                        On the other hand, we denounce with righteous indignation and dislike men who are so beguiled and demoralized by the charms of pleasure of the moment, so blinded by desire, that they cannot foresee the pain and trouble that are bound to ensue;
                        <LineBreak />
                        <LineBreak />
                        equal blame belongs to those who fail in their duty through weakness of will, which is the same as saying through shrinking from toil and pain. These cases are perfectly simple and easy to distinguish. In a free hour, when our power of choice is untrammelled and when nothing prevents our being able to do what we like best, every pleasure is to be welcomed and every pain avoided. But in certain circumstances and owing to the claims of duty or the obligations of business it will frequently occur that pleasures have to be repudiated and annoyances accepted. The wise man therefore always holds in these matters to this principle of selection: he rejects pleasures to secure other greater pleasures, or else he endures pains to avoid worse pains.
                    </TextBlock>
                </Grid>
                <RichTextBox Margin="0,10,0,0" Padding="4" AcceptsReturn="True" IsDocumentEnabled="True"
                             IsReadOnly="True"
                             VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" SpellCheck.IsEnabled="False"
                             materialDesign:HintAssist.Hint="Multiline text"
                             MaxHeight="120" x:Name="DescriptionTextBox">
                    <RichTextBox.Resources>
                        <Style TargetType="{x:Type Border}">
                            <Setter Property="CornerRadius" Value="4" />
                        </Style>
                    </RichTextBox.Resources>
                </RichTextBox>
                <TextBox
                    x:Name="InputTextBox"
                    Margin="0,10,0,0"
                    Padding="4,4,10,4"
                    VerticalAlignment="Center"
                    Foreground="{DynamicResource MaterialDesign.Brush.Foreground}" />
            </StackPanel>
            <StackPanel.ContextMenu>
                <ContextMenu Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignContextMenu}">
                    <ContextMenu.Resources>
                        <Style TargetType="{x:Type MenuItem}"
                               BasedOn="{StaticResource MaterialDesignMenuItem}" />
                    </ContextMenu.Resources>
                    <MenuItem Header="复制 (_C)" Command="{Binding Path=CopyMessageTextCommand}" />
                </ContextMenu>
            </StackPanel.ContextMenu>
        </StackPanel>

        <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal" HorizontalAlignment="Right" VerticalAlignment="Bottom" Margin="0 0 10 10">
            <Button Style="{DynamicResource MaterialDesignFlatButton}" HorizontalAlignment="Left"
                    x:Name="OfficialLauncherButton" Margin="5,0,0,0" Click="OfficialLauncherButton_Click">
                <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                    <materialDesign:PackIcon Kind="Launch" />
                    <TextBlock Margin="8 0 0 0" VerticalAlignment="Center" Text="官方启动器" />
                </StackPanel>
            </Button>
            <Button Style="{DynamicResource MaterialDesignFlatButton}" HorizontalAlignment="Left"
                    x:Name="DiscordButton" Margin="5,0,0,0" Click="DiscordButton_Click">
                <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                    <mahIcon:PackIconSimpleIcons Kind="Discord" />
                    <TextBlock Margin="8 0 0 0" VerticalAlignment="Center" Text="Discord" />
                </StackPanel>
            </Button>
            <Button Style="{DynamicResource MaterialDesignFlatButton}" HorizontalAlignment="Left"
                    x:Name="NewGitHubIssueButton" Margin="5,0,0,0" Click="NewGitHubIssueButton_OnClick">
                <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                    <materialDesign:PackIcon Kind="Github" />
                    <TextBlock Margin="8 0 0 0" VerticalAlignment="Center" Text="GitHub" />
                </StackPanel>
            </Button>
            <Button Style="{DynamicResource MaterialDesignFlatButton}" HorizontalAlignment="Left"
                    x:Name="IntegrityReportButton" Margin="5,0,0,0" Click="IntegrityReportButton_Click">
                <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                    <materialDesign:PackIcon Kind="FileDocument" />
                    <TextBlock Margin="8 0 0 0" VerticalAlignment="Center" Text="完整性报告" />
                </StackPanel>
            </Button>
            <Button Style="{DynamicResource MaterialDesignFlatButton}" HorizontalAlignment="Left"
                    x:Name="PackTroubleshooting" Margin="5,0,0,0" Click="PackTroubleshooting_OnClick"
                    Visibility="{Binding PackTroubleshootingVisibility}">
                <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                    <materialDesign:PackIcon Kind="Bug" />
                    <TextBlock Margin="8 0 0 0" VerticalAlignment="Center" Text="打包日志" />
                </StackPanel>
            </Button>
            <Button x:Name="Button1" Margin="5,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Right" Click="Button1_Click"
                    Content="Button1" MinWidth="80" />
            <Button x:Name="Button2" Margin="5,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Right" Click="Button2_Click"
                    Content="Button2" MinWidth="80" />
            <Button x:Name="Button3" Margin="5,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Right" Click="Button3_Click"
                    Content="Button3" MinWidth="80" />
        </StackPanel>
    </Grid>
</Window>
